      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Double VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides a direct, mechanical connection to the M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a suspension setup that retains its factory-intended damping and rebound characteristics. This is a mechanically robust example of the ultimate driving machine, offering the precise turn-in and linear power delivery that defines the platform.",
